<p></p><div class="quoteright" style="width:350px;"><div class="lazy_load_img_box" style="padding-top:142.86%"><img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/images/world_treasury_of_science_fiction.png" class="embeddedimage" border="0" alt="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/images/world_treasury_of_science_fiction.png" width="350" height="500"></div></div>First published in 1989 by editor <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/DavidGHatwell" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/DavidGHatwell">David G Hatwell</a>, this <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GenreAnthology" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GenreAnthology">Genre Anthology</a> contains over fifty stories, chosen from all over the world.<p></p><h3>Works in this anthology:</h3><div class="proper-ad-unit mobile-ad square_ad"><h6 class="ad-caption">Advertisement:</h6><div id="proper-ad-tvtropes_mobile_ad_1"><script>propertag.cmd.push(function() { proper_display('tvtropes_mobile_ad_1'); })</script></div></div><ul><li> "<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/HarrisonBergeron" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/HarrisonBergeron">Harrison Bergeron</a>", by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/KurtVonnegutJr" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/KurtVonnegutJr">Kurt Vonnegut, Jr.</a> (1961, English)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Forgetfulness" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/Forgetfulness">Forgetfulness</a>", by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/JohnWCampbell" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/JohnWCampbell">John W. Campbell</a> (1937, English)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/SpecialFlight" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/SpecialFlight">Special Flight</a>", by <a class="createlink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/JohnBerryman" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/JohnBerryman">John Berryman</a> (1939, English)</li><li> "<a class="createlink" href="